Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT Id, Name, CAST(ISNULL(Valor1,0) AS int) AS Code FROM dbo.ParameterDetail WHERE ParameterId='main.ArticleGroup'

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: BEGIN DECLARE @result varchar(20) SET @result = @SequencePrefix + dbo.UFN_PadLeft(@SequenceId,'0',@SuffixLength) RETURN @result END

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value:
BEGIN DECLARE @OutputText VARCHAR(8000)
SET @OutputText = REPLICATE(@CharacterToPad, @NumberToPad) + @TextToPad
RETURN RIGHT(@OutputText, @NumberToPad) END
